== Events == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1641]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate relocated Dutch residents from Hirado to the artificial island of {{ill|Dejima|ja|出島|12=draft|12=draft}} in Nagasaki. * [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1809]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mamiya Rinzō|ja|間宮林蔵|12=draft|12=draft}} crossed alone to Sakhalin, proving that it was indeed an island; the strait was thereafter named the {{ill|Mamiya Kaikyō|ja|間宮海峡|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1870]] {{ill|June 15|ja|6月15日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Tondenhei colonists began to settle Hokkaidō.
