== Events == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1641]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate relocated Dutch residents from Hirado to the artificial island of {{ill|Dejima|ja|出島|qq=}} in Nagasaki. * [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1809]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mamiya Rinzō|ja|間宮林蔵|qq=}} crossed alone to Sakhalin, proving that it was indeed an island; the strait was thereafter named the {{ill|Mamiya Kaikyō|ja|間宮海峡|qq=}}. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1870]] {{ill|June 15|ja|6月15日|qq=}}) – Tondenhei colonists began to settle Hokkaidō.
== Births == * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1668]] {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Amamori Hōshū|ja|雨森芳洲|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar (died [[1755]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1865]] {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Murakami Onikijō|ja|村上鬼城|qq=}}, a haiku poet (died [[1938]]). * 慶応1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} 1865, June 10) – {{ill|Koizumi Matashirō|ja|小泉又次郎|qq=}}, a politician (died [[1951]]). * 慶応2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1866]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kōkusun Junjirō|ja|高楠順次郎|qq=}}, a Buddhist scholar (died [[1945]]).
== Deaths == * [[Huangchu]] 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[226]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Cao Pi|ja|曹丕|qq=}} (Wen Emperor), the first Emperor of Wei in the Three Kingdoms period, and son of {{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|qq=}} (born [[187]]). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1778]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Nagaya Sōen|ja|永谷宗円|qq=}}, a village headman and developer of the blue-steeped sencha brewing method (born [[1681]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kozeki Sanei|ja|小関三英|qq=}}, a physician and Rangaku scholar (born [[1787]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Harada Sano-suke|ja|原田左之助|qq=}}, a member of the [[Shinsengumi|新選組]] (birth year unknown).
