'''May 17''' is the 17th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1641]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate relocated Dutch residents from Hirado to the artificial island of {{ill|Dejima|ja|出島|qq=|12=draft}} in Nagasaki.
* [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1809]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mamiya Rinzō|ja|間宮林蔵|qq=|12=draft}} crossed alone to Sakhalin, proving that it was indeed an island; the strait was thereafter named the {{ill|Mamiya Kaikyō|ja|間宮海峡|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1870]] {{ill|June 15|ja|6月15日|qq=|12=draft}}) – Tondenhei colonists began to settle Hokkaidō.

== Births ==
