* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1865]] {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Murakami Onikijō|ja|村上鬼城|qq=|12=draft}}, a haiku poet (died [[1938]]).
