== Deaths == * [[Huangchu]] 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[226]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Cao Pi|ja|曹丕|qq=|12=draft}} (Wen Emperor), the first Emperor of Wei in the Three Kingdoms period, and son of {{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|qq=|12=draft}} (born [[187]]). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1778]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Nagaya Sōen|ja|永谷宗円|qq=|12=draft}}, a village headman and developer of the blue-steeped sencha brewing method (born [[1681]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kozeki Sanei|ja|小関三英|qq=|12=draft}}, a physician and Rangaku scholar (born [[1787]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Harada Sano-suke|ja|原田左之助|qq=|12=draft}}, a member of the [[Shinsengumi|新選組]] (birth year unknown).
