== Events == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1641]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 25|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate relocated Dutch residents from Hirado to the artificial island of {{ill|Dejima|ja|出島|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dejima|qq=}} in Nagasaki. * [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1809]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mamiya Rinzō|ja|間宮林蔵|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mamiya Rinzō|qq=}} crossed alone to Sakhalin, proving that it was indeed an island; the strait was thereafter named the {{ill|Mamiya Kaikyō|ja|間宮海峡|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mamiya Kaikyō|qq=}}. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1870]] {{ill|June 15|ja|6月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 15|qq=}}) – Tondenhei colonists began to settle Hokkaidō.
